# Skill Loopback Governance

## After Significant Fixes
- Update `docs/documentation-manager/lessons-learned.md`.
- Update or add a command log entry under `docs/documentation-manager/commands/`.

## Skill Update Policy
- Do not silently rewrite broad skills on every task.
- When a repeated pattern or mistake is identified:
  1) propose a focused skill/rule update
  2) apply update after user confirmation

## Anti-Regression Focus
- Capture root cause and prevention rule.
- Keep prevention rules concise and actionable.
- Link updates to affected case docs (`admin`, `user`, `organization`) when relevant.
